Performance:

Use Nuxt Image module: deliver AVIF/WEBP, set sizes for responsive images.

Preload key hero image and fonts; use font-display: swap.

Defer non-critical JS; avoid heavy client libraries.

Cache serverless responses on Vercel (Cache-Control s-maxage & stale-while-revalidate).

Lighthouse targets: LCP < 2.5s, FID (or TTFB) minimal, CLS < 0.1.

Accessibility:

All images have alt.

Color contrast >= 4.5:1 for body text, WCAG AA.

Keyboard navigable header and forms.

Use semantic HTML for hours, address (<address>), and lists.

Security:

CSP headers (Vercel header config or middleware).

Rate-limit contact form or use captcha.


All pages must be responsive (desktop, tablet, mobile).

Use Tailwind spacing & utility classes for consistency.

Optimize images with Nuxt Image.

Add SEO meta tags + structured data (LocalBusiness) on Home + Contact.

Accessibility: alt text for all images, high color contrast, keyboard nav.

Performance: lazy-load non-critical images, prefetch routes.